{
  "id": "5cbea6e6eb02ea0017af8d4d",
  "title": "建設的相互作用",
  "created": 1555998443,
  "updated": 1556175808,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cbea6e6eb02ea0017af8d4d",
      "text": "建設的相互作用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998443,
      "updated": 1555998443
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbea71daff09e0000f6f8f3",
      "text": "[素朴理論]と[建設的相互作用]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998493,
      "updated": 1555998503
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbea72baff09e0000f6f8f4",
      "text": " \t[教育心理学概論]に書かれているらしい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998508,
      "updated": 1556175099
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbea735aff09e0000f6f8f5",
      "text": "\t[カイゼンジャーニー] P.52",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998517,
      "updated": 1555998524
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbea74daff09e0000f6f8f6",
      "text": "\t後で詳しく調べる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998542,
      "updated": 1555998544
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbea6ebaff09e0000f6f8f2",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/7126250c869544c2c85cf180aecd82b1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998443,
      "updated": 1555998488
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbea717aff09e0000a57802",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555998488,
      "updated": 1555998488
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15bbcaff09e0000160967",
      "text": "原典に当たった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175805,
      "updated": 1556175808
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc158b9aff09e0000160950",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a4d3741034c4c0373351339cd97c8824]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175033,
      "updated": 1556175085
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc158ecaff09e0000d1fa2a",
      "text": "\t[教育心理学概論] P.15",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175085,
      "updated": 1556175118
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15907aff09e0000160951",
      "text": "\t[知識]と[理解]の[社会的構成]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175112,
      "updated": 1556175135
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15912aff09e0000160952",
      "text": "\t文脈",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175123,
      "updated": 1556175150
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc1592eaff09e0000160954",
      "text": "\t\t子供は素朴理論を持っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175150,
      "updated": 1556175156
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15958aff09e0000160956",
      "text": "\t\t抽象度の高い科学的概念は子供が直接経験しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175193,
      "updated": 1556175755
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15960aff09e0000160957",
      "text": "\t\t\t「物体は力が加わらなければ等速運動をする」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175201,
      "updated": 1556175231
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15980aff09e0000160958",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t実際に観察するものは「ボールを投げたら曲がって飛ぶ」「転がしたボールはそのうち止まる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175232,
      "updated": 1556175265
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc159a5aff09e0000160959",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「物体に力が加わらない」という状況がレアだから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175269,
      "updated": 1556175284
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc159ebaff09e000016095a",
      "text": "\t\t学校で先生が「わかりやすい説明」をすると、「[バブル型理解]」が発生してしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175340,
      "updated": 1556175508
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15a34aff09e000016095c",
      "text": "\t\t\tそれだけが独立した、経験則とつながらない理解",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175412,
      "updated": 1556175426
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15a42aff09e000016095d",
      "text": "\t\t\tこういう知識はすぐ消えてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175426,
      "updated": 1556175463
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15a95aff09e000016095f",
      "text": "\t\tこれらの科学的概念は議論、仮説、実験をへて「社会的構成」された",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175509,
      "updated": 1556175509
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15a95aff09e0000160960",
      "text": "\t\t\tこの「社会的構成」を、学習の場での「[対話]」によって行う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175509,
      "updated": 1556175657
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15ac9aff09e0000160961",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれがこの本の伝えたい「学びのモデル」である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175561,
      "updated": 1556175569
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc1592eaff09e0000160953",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175150,
      "updated": 1556175150
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15b0eaff09e0000160962",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175630,
      "updated": 1556175630
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15b0eaff09e0000160963",
      "text": "\t[抽象化]とも関連している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175630,
      "updated": 1556175636
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15b0eaff09e0000160964",
      "text": "\t\t[抽象的な知識をどうやって獲得するのか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175631,
      "updated": 1556175644
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15b1aaff09e0000160965",
      "text": "\t[対話の場を作る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175642,
      "updated": 1556175743
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc15b7caff09e0000160966",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556175740,
      "updated": 1556175740
    }
  ]
}